th":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/py8mI1nIFOvnPksi0sv6t5LoTF5.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/aBlQQanWoYKi63wl3kZ7i2I5nVo.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/v2eyymeuXShRgqcTEZo7ZL0OncX.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/uyr2XKXKq37kzFhv090LhwepcNn.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/oFWlkrCLoG6q2UInCdJb0P6UPAp.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/uDI9rMPwyWYqCDhP5eqBnSOArDM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/unRpgz6OFUmIVvgyOqFmBE0CwVF.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/msPzeb1x9c8BnqGdk8E2IxnrQ4Q.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:13:36.605+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"连年亏损的民间马戏团被团长连人带物贱卖给奸商，其中宫兰兰和阿丽以及其他团员在新老板大金牙的忽悠下，一同登船开启了去泰国巡演的旅途。 行至东南亚热带雨林途中，突然遭遇了神秘巨蟒的袭击，他们搭救了一个名叫杰夫的神秘男子。可接连的巨蟒袭击造成船体沉没，杰夫提出带众人穿过雨林去找他的船，却不料这个男人的真实身份竟然是“偷猎者”。蒙在鼓里的马戏团等人就此踏上一条充满血腥的热带雨林之旅……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A struggling circus crew gets deceived by its former partner, as it embarks on a tour in Thailand. During the journey through a Southeast Asian rainforest, they encounter attacks by a giant python. They meet a mysterious man named Jeff who offers to help, but they soon realize he's a poacher. As they search for Jeff's boat, they face life-and-death struggles with the python and Jeff himself."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"狂蟒之災 2024","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"聯年虧損的民間馬戲團被團長聯人帶物賤賣給奸商，其中宮蘭蘭和阿麗以及其他團員在新老闆大金牙的忽悠下，一同登船開啟了去泰國巡演的旅途。\r 行至東南亞熱帶雨林途中，突然遭遇了神秘巨蟒的襲擊，他們搭救了一個名叫傑夫的神秘男子。可接聯的巨蟒襲擊造成船體沉沒，傑夫提議帶眾人穿過雨林去找他的船，卻不料這個男人的真實身份竟然是「偷獵者」。蒙在鼓裏的馬戲團等人就此踏上充滿血腥的熱帶雨林之旅…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"大蟒蛇：奪命森林","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"連年虧損的民間馬戲團被團長連人帶物賤賣給奸商，其中宮蘭蘭和阿麗以及其他團員在新老闆大金牙的忽悠下，一同登船開啓了去泰國巡演的旅途。 行至東南亞熱帶雨林途中，突然遭遇了神祕巨蟒的襲擊，他們搭救了一個名叫傑夫的神祕男子。可接連的巨蟒襲擊造成船體沈沒，傑夫提出帶眾人穿過雨林去找他的船，卻不料這個男人的真實身份竟然是「偷獵者」。蒙在鼓裡的馬戲團等人就此踏上一條充滿血腥的熱帶雨林之旅……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O filme acompanha um circo em dificuldades, enganado por seu ex-parceiro, ao embarcar em uma turnê pela Tailândia. Durante a viagem por uma floresta tropical do Sudeste Asiático, eles encontram ataques de uma sucuri gigante."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Вербувани от свой стар познат, група циркови артисти се отправят на път, с цел да изнесат представлението на живота си. Качени на лодка те навлизат дълбоко в тропическите гори на Тайланд, където се натъкват на безскрупулен ловец на змии, чиято цел ще ги въвлече в битка за оцеляване."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un equipo de circo en apuros es engañado por un ex socio, mientras se embarca en una gira por Tailandia. Durante el viaje a través de una selva tropical del sudeste asiático, se enfrenta al ataque de una pitón gigante. Conocen a un hombre misterioso llamado Jeff que se ofrece a ayudar, pero pronto se dan cuenta de que es un cazador furtivo. Mientras buscan el barco de Jeff, se enfrentan a vida o muerte con la pitón y el propio Jeff."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Remake akcijske grozljivke iz leta 1997. Na turneji po Tajski cirkuško ekipo, ki se bori s težavami, prevara njen nekdanji partner. Med potjo po deževnem gozdu jugovzhodne Azije naletijo na napade ogromnega pitona. Spoznajo skrivnostnega moža po imenu Jeff, ki jim ponudi pomoč. Med iskanjem Jeffove ladje, se spopadajo s pitonom in samim Jeffom na življenje in smrt."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Předělávka akčního hororu (Anakonda) z roku 1997 o skupině dokumentaristů, kteří pátrají po obřím smrtícím hadovi v Amazonii."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda: Hutan Terkutuk","runtime":80,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sekelompok atlet sirkus, dalam perjalanan menuju lokasi pertunjukan baru yang mereka kira, terdampar di hutan hujan lebat setelah perahu yang mereka tumpangi hancur akibat serangan anaconda. Mereka berpapasan dengan seorang pemburu liar berbahaya yang sedang memburu ular tersebut dan menyadari bahwa ia mungkin kini memiliki cukup umpan untuk menangkapnya. Untungnya, sebagai pemain sirkus, mereka memiliki beberapa trik"},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"อนาคอนดา ป่าอาถรรพ์","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"สมาชิกคณะละครสัตว์ที่กำลังประสบ ปัญหา รวมทั้งหลานหลาน กง และอาลี ถูกชักจูงโดยเจ้านายคนใหม่ผู้โลภมาก บิ๊กโกลด์ทูธ ให้ไปเดินสายแสดงใน ประเทศไทย ขณะเดินทางผ่านป่าฝน ในเอเชียตะวันออกเฉียงใต้ พวกเขาถูก จู่โจมโดยอนาคอนด้าลึกลับ แต่ สามารถช่วยชีวิตชายแปลกหน้าชื่อว่า เจฟฟ์ไว้ได้ เจฟฟ์ ผู้ซึ่งแท้จริงแล้วเป็น พรานเถื่อน นำคณะละครสัตว์เข้าสู่การ เดินทางโชกเลือดในป่าเขตร้อนที่แสน อันตราย..."},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Цирковая труппа отправляется в тропические джунгли в поисках новой площадки для выступлений. Вскоре артисты понимают, что их проводник — сумасшедший браконьер, решивший использовать их в качестве наживки для гигантской анаконды."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda: Khu Rừng Nguyền Rủa","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bị kẹt lại trong khu rừng nhiệt đới, một nhóm nghệ sĩ xiếc phải tìm cách thoát khỏi con trăn khổng lồ ghê rợn và tên săn trộm cuồng săn có âm mưu tàn nhẫn."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Anaconda Cursed Jungle","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La troupe d’un cirque embarque sur un bateau et traverse la jungle thaïlandaise. Mais leur voyage sera contrarié par un anaconda géant…"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"아나콘다: 저주받은 정글","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"태국 순회 공연을 시작한 한 서커스 팀이 전 동료에게 속아넘어간다. 동남아시아 열대우림을 가로지르는 여정 중, 그들은 거대한 비단뱀의 공격을 받는다. 도움을 제안하는 제프라는 신비한 남자를 만나지만, 그가 밀렵꾼임을 곧 깨닫게 된다. 제프의 배를 찾아 나선 그들은 비단뱀과 제프 자신과의 생사를 건 싸움에 직면한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":15608,"adult":false,"title":"Tiësto in Concert","video":true,"overview":"Tiësto in Concert is a performance of Tiësto's concert on May 10, 2003, at the Gelredome in Arnhem, Gelderland, Netherlands, when he performed before an audience of over 25,000 people. The concert was divided into parties with live performances by groups, bands and artists representing a country, which in turn represented a continent. It begins with a presentation by Tiësto followed by a live performance by Andain who presents to Britain and Europe. Then, a group of carnival Sanba presents to Brazil and South America. The singer's live performance and band Dinand Woesthoff presents \"The Star-Spangled Banner\" to the United States. The Chinese group Orange Studio performs the theme \"Tiësto in Concert Asia\", presented to countries there. After a live performance by singer Jan Johnston, Omar Ka & Fula Band presents to Africa, and finally, the live performance of Jerry de Jonge & Beijerink presents to Australia and Oceania. A Bluray version with the Director's Cut was released in 2012.","genre_ids":[10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0663,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/eRT4NSoebjqRxvqeVa2oVt0GkT4.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-02","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/4CA7A5aPyrU1nfKNftVWof5Q0ug.jpg","original_title":"Tiësto in Concert","original_language":"es"},{"id":1319482,"adult":false,"title":"Traumatika","video":false,"overview":"Mikey's night terrors become reality when his mother begins showing signs of demonic possession. What he's about to experience will haunt him for the rest of his life and claim countless lives across generations.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4017,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/jnINnXC7KHAVodspt9xIepEE9f6.jpg","release_date":"2025-11-13","vote_average":4.778,"backdrop_path":"/gdVOvkG10Axz7mYnucVbzT9uT8O.jpg","original_title":"Traumatika","original_language":"en"},{"id":1271622,"adult":false,"title":"WWE King and Queen of the Ring","video":true,"overview":"The 2024 King & Queen of the Ring was a professional wrestling event produced by the American company WWE. It was the 12th King of the Ring event and took place on May 25, 2024, at the Jeddah Super Dome in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. It aired via pay-per-view (PPV) and live streaming and wrestlers from the Raw and SmackDown brand divisions. This was the first King of the Ring to livestream on the WWE Network since the 2015 event, the first to livestream on Peacock, and the first to air on PPV since the 2002 event.  It was the 11th event that WWE held in Saudi Arabia under a 10-year partnership supporting Saudi Vision 2030. The event will also see the finals of both the King of the Ring tournament and the second Queen's Crown tournament.","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2329,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/wthcQM6OdsO8mAehmFmOoPiRT1O.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-25","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/l2wmrV7i9IDNBxY9DqRomg6KaCT.jpg","original_title":"WWE King and Queen of the Ring","original_language":"en"},{"id":1429747,"adult":false,"title":"Same Day with Someone","video":false,"overview":"Trapped in a time loop, a picture-perfect museum curator relives her worst day ever and must figure out how to break free from the vicious cycle.","genre_ids":[10749,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0764,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/u36O7Sdbo34PIj0uN6C2671eaMJ.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-17","vote_average":7.875,"backdrop_path":"/9ibwr02TiPvxN1jqLufKXvFVD1Y.jpg","original_title":"ซ้ำวัน กับ Someone","original_language":"th"},{"id":318945,"adult":false,"title":"Twenty Something","video":false,"overview":"Young friends (Jordan Chan, Moses Chan, Farini Cheung) look for happiness but find only fleeting pleasure in barhopping and one-night stands.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4653,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/kZb146RKzGXodebhJIBgdaWbL3j.jpg","release_date":"1994-04-08","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"晚9朝5","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1168720,"adult":false,"title":"Man-Eating Shark","video":false,"overview":"A group of poachers hunted sharks indiscriminately on the high seas, angering the great white shark, and the poachers died in the shark's mouth. In turn, the great white shark focuses on the five friends on the yacht celebrating graduation, so the five of them fought fiercely with the great white shark. Between life and death, only the idea of ​​escaping from the shark's mouth and returning to the shore can continue to support them...","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.153,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/w0z9svd5AVEwNWiYUJgFtw3zu80.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/kPhkrHmNvfKdf1quqOZTPY1uTib.jpg","original_title":"食人鲨","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1244999,"adult":false,"title":"Stans","video":false,"overview":"A revealing, edgy, and disarmingly personal journey into the world of superfandom, told through the lens of one of the world's most iconic and enduring artists, Eminem, and the fans that worship him.","genre_ids":[99,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9882,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/jqIvV9wWIA5h1UREfCcnBBlcr6Q.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-06","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/cY6IXwtmc8xdznDlw2eegB8OGx1.jpg","original_title":"Stans","original_language":"en"},{"id":1389158,"adult":false,"title":"Maa","video":false,"overview":"A mother and daughter encounter a demon in a village where girls have been disappearing.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0888,"vote_count":57,"poster_path":"/kc5n7LJUmvBsVxzAla1ONN8kouP.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-20","vote_average":6.807,"backdrop_path":"/u3Cfe21Cmv5cWs5VnFCz15HdfKO.jpg","original_title":"माँ","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1272228,"adult":false,"title":"Underdog","video":false,"overview":"Two Tarahumara brothers, with a deep spiritual connection and a fervent desire to become the best ultramarathon runners in the world, will see their dreams shattered when they are violently recruited by a dangerous cartel as drug runners, putting their family at risk and forcing them to join forces to finally take control of their own destiny.","genre_ids":[18,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3536,"vote_count":66,"poster_path":"/sXTlI8tWGmB2CL8OQZsjMZvj1cb.jpg","release_date":"2024-04-25","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/7xi9no1b8FiTeUSix9zf9UalhXw.jpg","original_title":"Correr Para Vivir","original_language":"es"},{"id":852432,"adult":false,"title":"The Tower","video":false,"overview":"In the heart of a city, the inhabitants of a tower wake up one morning to find that their building is shrouded in an opaque fog, obstructing doors and windows - a strange dark matter that devours anything that tries to pass through it. Trapped, the residents try to organize themselves, but to ensure their survival they gradually succumb to their most primitive instincts, until they sink into horror...","genre_ids":[27,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6458,"vote_count":133,"poster_path":"/9wcvKsdNs5eImAYFD4b12d0fSs9.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-08","vote_average":4.816,"backdrop_path":"/zRXJARKQZk6NleofIEyWcBt1fGk.jpg","original_title":"La Tour","original_language":"fr"},{"id":567566,"adult":false,"title":"The Rifleman","video":false,"overview":"The love story of sixteen-year-old Arturs is interrupted by the First World War. After losing his mother and his home, he finds some consolation in joining the army, because this is the first time national battalions are allowed in the Russian Empire. But war is nothing like Arturs imagined – no glory, no fairness. It is brutal and painful. Arturs is now completely alone as war takes the lives of his father and brother. Also, no progress is made in the promised quick resolution of the war and timely return home. Within the notion that only he alone cares about returning home and that his homeland is just a playground for other nations, Arturs finds strength for the final battle and eventually returns home to start everything from scratch, just like his newly born country.","genre_ids":[10752,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6944,"vote_count":169,"poster_path":"/z3lVSySBEW17JK4k5RZJ5mALHM5.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-11","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/hxPi9FOd46WEVajcjhON8m3sihG.jpg","original_title":"Dvēseļu putenis","original_language":"lv"},{"id":14863,"adult":false,"title":"Anaconda 3: Offspring","video":false,"overview":"A mercenary-for-hire accepts a mission from a billionaire to capture a dangerous snake that could possibly help cure a terminal illness.","genre_ids":[27,12,53,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4283,"vote_count":361,"poster_path":"/qQzn9r0dy4TWoRMsVHk5iBuwVyK.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-23","vote_average":4.648,"backdrop_path":"/zkJCffPgcu7MWCyal0qGV4yCNMG.jpg","original_title":"Anaconda 3: Offspring","original_language":"en"},{"id":45650,"adult":false,"title":"The Hole","video":false,"overview":"After moving into a new neighbourhood, brothers Dane &amp; Lucas and their neighbour Julie discover a bottomless hole in the basement of their home. They find that once the hole is exposed, evil is unleashed. With strange shadows lurking around every corner and nightmares coming to life, they are forced to come face to face with their darkest fears to put an end to the mystery of THE HOLE.","genre_ids":[53,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.204,"vote_count":750,"poster_path":"/tQMxsrsVtpB2D2n01nUqgOMmSWD.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-12","vote_average":5.76,"backdrop_path":"/zK4ST48F7pmhBmMILhv6vvQO4n4.jpg","original_title":"The Hole","original_language":"en"},{"id":1241674,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Breath","video":false,"overview":"A group of old college friends reunite on a Caribbean scuba diving trip exploring the wreckage of a WWII battleship and find themselves trapped inside the underwater labyrinth of rusted metal surrounded by great white sharks.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9739,"vote_count":151,"poster_path":"/aC892vhMsNwcIUX5UfrsTSy9IL9.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-28","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/4wXTv2LhZrVWIyIHG4dVIsjxCon.jpg","original_title":"The Last Breath","original_language":"en"},{"id":18289,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla vs. Biollante","video":false,"overview":"After the previous Godzilla attack, a miniature arms race ensues to collect his cells. Concerned over Godzilla's possible return, the Japanese government uses the cells to create a new bio-weapon, ANEB (Anti-Nuclear Energy Bacteria). They seeks the aid of geneticist Genshiro Shiragami, who's experiments result in a new mutation.","genre_ids":[28,27,14,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9481,"vote_count":287,"poster_path":"/me4CanEAtNm03LXlFJOyhX3FsMF.jpg","release_date":"1989-12-16","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/wh832wXrqIVdSC5271fkJIuyji4.jpg","original_title":"ゴジラvsビオランテ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9360,"adult":false,"title":"Anaconda","video":false,"overview":"A 'National Geographic' film crew is taken hostage by an insane hunter, who takes them along on his quest to capture the world's largest — and deadliest — snake.","genre_ids":[12,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9877,"vote_count":2735,"poster_path":"/33NysOnLpLZY0ewHTcfpalzAsRG.jpg","release_date":"1997-04-11","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/e2oO1FPwMiDEi119rJJspYI6TiG.jpg","original_title":"Anaconda","original_language":"en"},{"id":290864,"adult":false,"title":"Kung Fu Jungle","video":false,"overview":"A martial arts instructor working at a police academy gets imprisoned after killing a man by accident. But when a vicious killer starts targeting martial arts masters, the instructor offers to help the police in return for his freedom.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2124,"vote_count":506,"poster_path":"/myZQ4WocOQQCXNGVJkHeeJ1jTEj.jpg","release_date":"2014-10-31","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/ezzptVQEg44CLDriFOE5TqEpXUf.jpg","original_title":"一個人的武林","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1012201,"adult":false,"title":"HAIKYU!! The Dumpster Battle","video":false,"overview":"Shoyo Hinata joins Karasuno High's volleyball club to be like his idol, a former Karasuno player known as the 'Little Giant'. But Hinata soon learns that he must team up with his middle school nemesis, Tobio Kageyama. Their clashing styles form a surprising weapon, but can their newfound teamwork defeat their rival Nekoma High in the highly anticipated 'Dumpster Battle', the long awaited ultimate showdown between two opposing underdog teams?","genre_ids":[16,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1952,"vote_count":228,"poster_path":"/ntRU0OA4etGGiMMmH1Yw0bnaMdW.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-16","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/cZmOrIOkJ2SNfVdiO85dUbOAYnL.jpg","original_title":"劇場版ハイキュー!! ゴミ捨て場の決戦","original_language":"ja"},{"id":11237,"adult":false,"title":"Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid","video":false,"overview":"A scientific expedition sets out for Borneo to seek a flower called the Blood Orchid, which could grant extended life. Meanwhile, they run afoul of snakes and each other.","genre_ids":[12,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2497,"vote_count":1081,"poster_path":"/apAZ6o1SyYgcC8R2LqTCYnBe1lK.jpg","release_date":"2004-08-25","vote_average":5.499,"backdrop_path":"/bMNHiwzjlg9FJNyxZ1zNFKZ9MTT.jpg","original_title":"Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid","original_language":"en"},{"id":9825,"adult":false,"title":"Lake Placid","video":false,"overview":"When a man is eaten alive by an unknown creature, the local Game Warden teams up with a paleontologist from New York to find the beast. Add to the mix an eccentric philanthropist with a penchant for \"Crocs\", and here we go! This quiet, remote lake is suddenly the focus of an intense search for a crocodile with a taste for live animals...and people!","genre_ids":[27,35,28,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2819,"vote_count":1221,"poster_path":"/pEszakCP8j9E9S0UPLfEa3Cad3O.jpg","release_date":"1999-07-15","vote_average":5.932,"backdrop_path":"/vvXc5WOBJQa3igNffSxMsqYyoqy.jpg","original_title":"Lake Placid","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":5503,"adult":false,"title":"The Fugitive","video":false,"overview":"Wrongfully convicted of murdering his wife and sentenced to death, Richard Kimble escapes from the law in an attempt to find the real killer and clear his name.","genre_ids":[28,53,18],"popularity":6.548,"vote_count":4674,"poster_path":"/b3rEtLKyOnF89mcK75G