 inside a police station that's about to be closed for good, officer Jake Roenick must cobble together a force made up cops and criminals to save themselves from a mob looking to kill mobster Marion Bishop.","genre_ids":[53,28,12,80],"popularity":1.5572,"vote_count":1172,"poster_path":"/oBpsRvMN1ONl8oFHuWt1rasDYFJ.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-19","vote_average":6.179,"backdrop_path":"/2c0Ls3EwFoWJWVqWuaMyCUAgmzD.jpg","original_title":"Assault on Precinct 13","original_language":"en"},{"id":9030,"adult":false,"title":"The Eye","video":false,"overview":"Violinist Sydney Wells was accidentally blinded by her sister Helen when she was five years old. She submits to a cornea transplantation, and while recovering from the operation, she realizes that she is seeing dead people.","genre_ids":[18,27,53],"popularity":2.826,"vote_count":1129,"poster_path":"/9N3znJ8sHH2EQjARCrUpxMj3hWd.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-01","vote_average":5.894,"backdrop_path":"/x5HfRp97ZoYbYTTBGA5JRrqbCZd.jpg","original_title":"The Eye","original_language":"en"},{"id":9036,"adult":false,"title":"Eight Below","video":false,"overview":"In the Antarctic, after an expedition with Dr. Davis McClaren, the sled dog trainer Jerry Shepherd has to leave the polar base with his colleagues due to the proximity of a heavy snow storm. He ties his dogs to be rescued after, but the mission is called-off and the dogs are left alone at their own fortune. For six months, Jerry tries to find a sponsor for a rescue mission.","genre_ids":[12,18,10751],"popularity":2.6895,"vote_count":1794,"poster_path":"/39hR806Me4wI42LCFcK2LBiCRGW.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-17","vote_average":7.035,"backdrop_path":"/1GAEBLa8EmA9d8l0s8gHB2zxWLq.jpg","original_title":"Eight Below","original_language":"en"},{"id":660335,"adult":false,"title":"Hunted","video":false,"overview":"A woman flees two serial killers who are hot on her heels in a forest.","genre_ids":[28,27,53],"popularity":3.5968,"vote_count":189,"poster_path":"/ytCQyuhipANedA1to4EKAOv10xv.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-03","vote_average":6.156,"backdrop_path":"/tdoqtxyeZLZUd12kZnUhnDvl8Q2.jpg","original_title":"Hunted","original_language":"en"},{"id":9009,"adult":false,"title":"Dark Water","video":false,"overview":"Dahlia and her five-year-old daughter are ready to begin a new life together. But their new apartment — dilapidated and worn — suddenly seems to take on a life of its own. Mysterious noises, persistent leaks of dark water and other strange happenings send Dahlia on a haunting and mystifying pursuit — one that unleashes a torrent of living nightmares.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"popularity":1.5985,"vote_count":1095,"poster_path":"/cm4M9xaBu78IjuAVNG4LCXdXsg.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-08","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/XKZjyePvRYPn7JdfRGZO3Q87qu.jpg","original_title":"Dark Water","original_language":"en"},{"id":9509,"adult":false,"title":"Man on Fire","video":false,"overview":"Jaded ex-CIA operative John Creasy reluctantly accepts a job as the bodyguard for a 10-year-old girl in Mexico City. They clash at first, but eventually bond, and when she's kidnapped he's consumed by fury and will stop at nothing to save her life.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":6.7485,"vote_count":5531,"poster_path":"/grCGLCcTHv9TChibzOwzUpykcjB.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-23","vote_average":7.457,"backdrop_path":"/6c7j7MQCczzNVvcrNEiXbs8Kt2p.jpg","original_title":"Man on Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":9373,"adult":false,"title":"The Texas Chainsaw Massacre","video":false,"overview":"After picking up a traumatized young hitchhiker, five friends find themselves stalked and hunted by a chainsaw-wielding killer and his family of equally psychopathic killers.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":5.3931,"vote_count":2846,"poster_path":"/781px1eOtfVt1RdIsL4Dt1s3x7R.jpg","release_date":"2003-05-21","vote_average":6.302,"backdrop_path":"/joj4ONoHmLGDoNGYph8ZPISphZ.jpg","original_title":"The Texas Chainsaw Massacre","original_language":"en"},{"id":9378,"adult":false,"title":"Thir13en Ghosts","video":false,"overview":"Arthur and his two children inherit his uncle's estate: a glass house that serves as a prison to twelve ghosts. When the family, accompanied by a nanny and an attorney, enter the house they find themselves trapped inside an evil machine 'designed by the Devil and powered by the dead' to open the Eye of Hell. Aided by a ghost hunter and his rival, a ghost rights activist out to set the ghosts free, the group must do what they can to get out of the house alive.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":8.1077,"vote_count":2314,"poster_path":"/6yrrddjIjx0ElCRZp5pTZeqrj3k.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-26","vote_average":6.285,"backdrop_path":"/mUffUjlJ007XAzdogdZqhaqSp4O.jpg","original_title":"Thir13en Ghosts","original_language":"en"},{"id":9313,"adult":false,"title":"The Man in the Iron Mask","video":false,"overview":"Years have passed since the Three Musketeers, Aramis, Athos and Porthos, have fought together with their friend, D'Artagnan. But with the tyrannical King Louis using his power to wreak havoc in the kingdom while his twin brother, Philippe, remains imprisoned, the Musketeers reunite to abduct Louis and replace him with Philippe.","genre_ids":[12,28,18],"popularity":3.4526,"vote_count":4066,"poster_path":"/tSLWIX3NzqFPWNMNX7FfeExHCRk.jpg","release_date":"1998-03-12","vote_average":6.645,"backdrop_path":"/uhhtglfXNaTavkKtjer38qHLfVi.jpg","original_title":"The Man in the Iron Mask","original_language":"en"},{"id":9341,"adult":false,"title":"The Core","video":false,"overview":"Geophysicist Dr. Josh Keyes discovers that an unknown force has caused the earth's inner core to stop rotating. With the planet's magnetic field rapidly deteriorating, our atmosphere literally starts to come apart at the seams with catastrophic consequences. To resolve the crisis, Keyes, along with a team of the world's most gifted scientists, travel into the earth's core. Their mission: detonate a device that will reactivate the core.","genre_ids":[878,12,53],"popularity":4.0981,"vote_count":2084,"poster_path":"/iMPR3OFhKNVvJw4eZoRhf9RzfHJ.jpg","release_date":"2003-03-28","vote_average":5.809,"backdrop_path":"/v2YxWPX2yKdo6arIAknJzKLxhZY.jpg","original_title":"The Core","original_language":"en"},{"id":9426,"adult":false,"title":"The Fly","video":false,"overview":"When Seth Brundle makes a huge scientific and technological breakthrough in teleportation, he decides to test it on himself. Unbeknownst to him, a common housefly manages to get inside the device and the two become one.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":5.6829,"vote_count":4848,"poster_path":"/8gZWMhJHRvaXdXsNhERtqNHYpH3.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-15","vote_average":7.428,"backdrop_path":"/cFnv7rB6I9gtZ0eTR7nPgjKNe0Q.jpg","original_title":"The Fly","original_language":"en"},{"id":9433,"adult":false,"title":"The Edge","video":false,"overview":"The plane carrying wealthy Charles Morse crashes down in the Alaskan wilderness. Together with the two other passengers, photographer Robert and assistant Stephen, Charles devises a plan to help them reach civilization. However, his biggest obstacle might not be the elements, or even the Kodiak bear stalking them -- it could be Robert, whom Charles suspects is having an affair with his wife and would not mind seeing him dead.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"popularity":2.6778,"vote_count":1280,"poster_path":"/zplJqfuUyqzW0D4jX3W1afl0d7b.jpg","release_date":"1997-09-06","vote_average":6.842,"backdrop_path":"/yU3nJxP2vNy8OQdDsfV09elG4k9.jpg","original_title":"The Edge","original_language":"en"},{"id":9306,"adult":false,"title":"The Island of Dr. Moreau","video":false,"overview":"A plane crash surviving attorney stumbles upon a mysterious island and is shocked to discover that a brilliant scientist and his lab assistant have found a way to combine human and animal DNA—with horrific results.","genre_ids":[878,27],"popularity":1.6023,"vote_count":551,"poster_path":"/hOJeQXve8W9rNRhdgC1WV3GQJyA.jpg","rele